  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Housing for families residing in buildings renovated in S&#xE3;o Paulo, Brazil</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Contribute to a housing policy for the central areas with a focus on sectors with lower income and for dialogue with government agencies at the local, state and federal levels. This will be done through evaluation of housing projects in central areas by civil society organizations and beneficiaries; emphasis on improvements in human and social development of families residing in buildings renovated; identification of public services for families in renovated buildings; evaluation of support in the social area for these families; and further support for movement of housing in central areas.</narrative>
  </description>
